    dc:description "FIGURE 2 Dolerocypris sisaketensis n. sp., female. A. RV, internal view (MSU-ZOC. 128); B. LV, internal view (ditto); C. anterior part of A; D. posterior part of A; E. posterior part of B; F. anterior part of B; G. carapace, left lateral view (MSU- ZOC. 131); H. carapace, dorsal view (ditto). Scale bar = 500 Μm for A – B; 310 Μm for C – F; 230 Μm for G – H." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/270572/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.270573>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3 Dolerocypris sisaketensis n. sp., female (MSU-ZOC. 128). A. A 1; B. A 2; C. distal part of penultimate segment and terminal segment; D. Md-palp; E. terminal segment of Md-palp; F. Md-coxa. Scale bar = 100 Μm for A – B, F; 50 Μm for C – E." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/270573/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.270574>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4 Dolerocypris sisaketensis n. sp., female (MSU-ZOC. 128). A. Mx 1; B. T 1; C. protopodite of T 1; D. T 2; E. T 3; F. caudal ramus; G. caudal ramus attachment. Scale bar = 54 Μm for A; 93 Μm for B; 50 Μm for C; 100 Μm for D – G." ;
